{"id":"onezapman-contract-xwp","title":"[EPIC] Lossless Subscription Platform","description":"Lossless Subscription Platform - Content creators earn from USDY yield while subscribers get principal back.\n\n**Core Mechanics:**\n- Fixed subscription: 100 USDT per content creator\n- USDY appreciation: 5% APY, calculated as ~0.416% monthly (fixed monthly growth)\n- No maximum lock period - subscriber decides when to unlock\n- Multiple subscriptions allowed (100 USDT per content creator)\n\n**Withdrawal Options:**\n1. Immediate: Pay 1 USDT penalty → Get ~99 USDT back\n2. Early (\u003c 30 days): Pay 0.5 USDT penalty → Get ~99.5 USDT back after 30 days\n3. Complete epoch (1 month): No penalty → Get 100 USDT back\n\n**Content Creator Registry:**\n- Self-registration: wallet + username\n- Fully updatable (wallet and username can be changed anytime)\n- Earnings: USDY yield + early withdrawal penalties\n\n**Internal Flow:**\nUSDT Lock → USDY Swap → Yield Accrues (monthly) → USDY→USDT Swap → Withdrawal","status":"closed","priority":0,"issue_type":"epic","owner":"fahmilukis04@gmail.com","created_at":"2026-01-14T06:33:51.798578904+07:00","created_by":"Fahmi","updated_at":"2026-01-14T06:50:56.418255041+07:00","closed_at":"2026-01-14T06:50:56.418255041+07:00","close_reason":"Closed"}
